<br>
You really think planar power is worth the effort?  You know stamina gains post 255 are miniscule, correct?  I definitely wouldn't put that ahead of any defensive AA, but that's just me.  Stats over 255 are horridly broken, and they are not nearly as valuable as a point under 255.<br>
<br>
Second, innate defense and LR are in fact 3 points per level, so that cuts down on the total quite a bit.<br>
<br>
Third, definitely pick up ambidex before you touch CF.  CF is a really miniscule damage increase, where as ambidex is fairly noticable if you have 2 half assed decent weapons.  Of course if you primarily use a 2 hander, like the current trend is moving, this is a null point.<br>
<br>
Fourth, if you tank with a 2 hander, double riposte is definitely not a waste of points, at least the first 2 levels (9 points).  I riposte quite a bit of hits, and a couple extra 300 hits adds up quick, even if they are few and far between.  With the recent findings on Ferocity and punishing blade and such, they're not all they're cracked up to be either.<br>
<br>
Fifth, castersrealm still hasn't fixed the stuff they said they're going to yet, so ya can't go by them quite yet, their information is massively outdated and incorrect.<br>
<br>
Stuff to think about.<br>
